              You've gotta be more clever when wiping your hard drive...<BR><BR>First, you wipe your hard drive with DBAN (Darik's Boot and Nuke at <A HREF="http://dban.sourceforge.net/)" TARGET=_blank>http://dban.sourceforge.net/)</A> to ensure that even the NSA couldn't recover traces of your P2P usage.<BR><BR>Then you reimage it with a fresh copy of Windows (legal, of course) and other apps (also legal), surf the web a bit, plant some files on there to make it look like it's been used, then hand the drive over to the lawyers and claim it's always been like that.

              

              
              
